javamoon.construct.source
Class CollectorEntityMethod

java.lang.Object
  javamoon.construct.source.CollectorAbstract
      javamoon.construct.source.CollectorEntityMethod
All Implemented Interfaces:
Collector
public class CollectorEntityMethod
extends CollectorAbstract

Second phase of the parsing. It collects the local entities and the method signatures and local decs. At the end of this process we have the following elements: attributes method signatures local decs

Version:
1.0
Author:
Raúl Marticorena

reset

public void reset()
Resets the state of the collector. It sets up the package as anonymous and removes the name of the current file. The reason is to begin the new phase without a package and file pre-established.
